org.osgeo.mapguide

Class MgCoordinateSystemMgrsGridSquarePosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgCoordinateSystemMgrsGridSquarePosition

  • public class MgCoordinateSystemMgrsGridSquarePosition
extends java.lang.Object
    MgCoordinateSystemMgrsGridSquarePosition defines enumerated values used to specify the the location desired relative to the subject MGRS grid sqaure when evaluating an MGRS string. Note that the values used in this enumeration match those used by the CS-MAP interface.
